=================================================================
= Info                                                          =
=================================================================
= The festival was founded in the year 2002 when the local team =
= of  the  town and the staff  of  Hard Rock Club  united their =
= efforts and thus  the  only annual open-air metal festival in =
= Estonia was born. Undoubtedly one  of  the smallest  on world =
= scale,  HRL  is the  largest  one  of  it's  kind in Estonia, =
= gathering  over  1000 metalheads  from  the  local scene, and =
= welcoming  visitors  from  Latvia  and  Lithuania, as well as =
= Finland and Sweden.                                           =
